title: Sabai ko lagi aayo jagat ma
lyrics:
Sabai ko lagi aayo jagat ma
Sabai ko lagi gariyo balidan -2
Apani jeevan lai Kalvari kruse ma -2
(A)
Yo timro jeevanko, euta saharo
Yo timro jeevanko, euta bato -2
Kohi paune chaina, Ishu jasto jagat ma -2
(B)
Yo timro jeevanko, euta maya
Yo timro jeevanko, euta mukti -2
Kohi de sakina, Ishu jasto nai jeevan -2
